15.A:
The current Spreadsheet module version you are using might not support ITA.
Follow the steps below to fix it.

① Log into the ITA Server.

② Download phpspreadsheet v1.18.0。
{cmd{# /usr/bin/composer.phar require "phpoffice/phpspreadsheet":"1.18.0"}command}

※ Input "n" when you are asked the following:
{cmd{No composer.json in current directory, do you want to use the one at /work? [Y,n]?}command}

③ Take a backup of the vendor directory.
{cmd{# mv /usr/share/php/vendor  [Free directory]}command}

④ Put the downloaded vendor directory (Step 2) under the /usr/share/php directory.
{cmd{# mv vendor /usr/share/php/}command}

